These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
Beverage: coffee, mirinda, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
Birthday: february, december, march, november
1. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left of Beverage:coffee##1
2. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Birthday:december is on the far left or far right##3
4. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Birthday:march##1
5. Birthday:november is between Birthday:december and Birthday:march##2
6. Beverage:almond-milk == Birthday:february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee     | hot-chocolate | mirinda |
| Birthday     | february     | march | november  | december      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
Job: dancer, security-guard, engineer, photographer
Movie-Genre: musical, mystery, zombie, epic
1. Job:security-guard is on the left of Movie-Genre:mystery##1
2. Movie-Genre:epic is on the far left or far right##3
3. Job:photographer is on the left of Movie-Genre:epic##1
4. Movie-Genre:epic is on the right of Movie-Genre:mystery##1
5. Job:engineer is on the far right##1
6. Movie-Genre:musical is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Job   | dancer | security-guard    | photographer     | engineer  |
| Movie-Genre     | musical    | zombie | mystery | epic |

